A [[currency_exchange]] site serving those trading between bitcoins and the following currencies:

* EURO
* USD
* LTC
* XRP

The service was launched June 07, 2011 (1.1). Trading against Second Life Lindens is no more available (1.2), due to change in Second Life ToS.

## Deposits and Withdrawing

Deposists methods available: SEPA transfers, OKPAY. TheRockTrading is also a Ripple gateway, which can be used to deposits BTC, LTC, EUR and USD, or even XRP. Lindens can be deposited via in-world ATMs, but can only be used for stock trading.

